  "notes": "Born c. 1550 in Gloucestershire, England — during the reign of Elizabeth I. Married Thomas Copp on February 28, 1576 in Hatton, Warwickshire. Son William Copp (1589-1670) emigrated to colonial Massachusetts. Died 1624 in Hatton, Warwickshire at approximately age 74. She lived through the entire Elizabethan era and into the reign of James I."
